data.description: Beautiful, turnkey two-story home in the gated community of the Heights at Five Knolls. This home has stunning features throughout including vaulted ceilings, tiled wood-like flooring, solar system, recessed lighting and plantation shutters. Lovely open floorplan with expansive kitchen, large island with quartz countertops, breakfast bar, butlers pantry and full walk-in pantry. Home boasts 4 comfortably sized bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, plus a half bath for guests on the lower level. Custom landscaping in front and rear yard with full drip system. Backyard has been fully remodeled with step up decking, bench seating, hot tub/spa & fountain water feature. Additional features include a 3 car garage, electric vehicle charging station, tankless water heater, indoor laundry room and much more. Wonderful community amenities include a sparkling pool and spa, fenced dog park, playground & clubhouse. Don't miss out on this great home!
